flowchart LR
    classDef dev    fill:#1565C0,color:#ffffff,stroke:#0D47A1,stroke-width:2px
    classDef ci     fill:#2E7D32,color:#ffffff,stroke:#1B5E20,stroke-width:2px
    classDef rel    fill:#E65100,color:#ffffff,stroke:#BF360C,stroke-width:2px
    classDef prod   fill:#4527A0,color:#ffffff,stroke:#311B92,stroke-width:2px
    classDef dep    fill:#00695C,color:#ffffff,stroke:#004D40,stroke-width:2px

    DEV["🔍 Development Profiling · Benchmarks Regression checks"]:::dev
    PR["🔎 Code Review Flag perf-sensitive changes for testing"]:::dev
    CI["⚙️ CI/CD Pipeline Automated load tests Threshold gates"]:::ci
    SCHED["📅 Regular Cadence Weekly full-scale tests Catch gradual regressions"]:::ci
    DEP["📦 Dependency Upgrades Dedicated perf pass Runtime · Library · Infra"]:::dep
    REL["🚀 Pre-Release Comprehensive suite All scenarios"]:::rel
    PROD["📡 Production Canary monitoring Ongoing trend tracking"]:::prod

    DEV --> PR --> CI --> SCHED --> REL --> PROD
    DEP --> REL
